                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>At the heart of AbbVie's unrelenting drive for innovation are the patients we serve. That's why our investment in R&amp;#x26;D is so critical. Our teams of scientists use novel approaches to help deliver therapies and solutions for conditions with the greatest unmet need.&lt;br> &lt;br> Through patient-focused drug development, we empower patient voices to be heard and help guide our decision-making process to advance cutting-edge science.&lt;/p>"/>
